  "title": "🥦 Kitchen Crew 👩‍🍳👨‍🍳",
  "description": "<p>📍 Location: CBD</p><p>💰 Salary: $2,100 – $2,400 / month</p><p>🕒 Hours: 44 hrs per week | 1 - 2 rest day (roster-based)</p><p>Shift Details (rotating weekly)</p><p>Morning Shift: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM</p><p>~8 working hours</p><p>Evening Shift: 12:00 PM – 9:30 PM</p><p><br />✨ What You’ll Be Doing:</p><p>- Help with food prep — chopping, portioning, and packing ingredients 🍱</p><p>- Maintain kitchen cleanliness and hygiene (you’ll be the unsung hero behind every healthy bowl!)</p><p>- Operate kitchen equipment safely</p><p>- Assist with loading and unloading ingredients</p><p>- Follow food safety standards (SFA / NEA compliance)</p><p>🙌 Who We’re Looking For:</p><p>- Able to carry heavy load, responsible, and punctual</p><p>- No experience needed — training provided!</p><p>- Enjoy working in a kitchen environment</p><p>🥗 Join a team that believes good food starts with good people!</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Nicholas Wong</p><p>EA Personnel No.: R23113643</p><p>EA Licence No.: 23C1703</p>",
